_:N2fe2ce6ce04849c69488570c35cacc02 <http://schema.org/description> "The Independent Adviser on Ministerial Standards is appointed by the Prime Minister to advise him on matters relating to the Ministerial Code. The post holder is independent of government and expected to provide impartial advice to the Prime Minister. IAMS works with the Cabinet Office ." .
